							<h5>underwriting</h5>
							The underwriting on either a binding authority or cedant review involves a complete examination of all activities including risk acceptance, rating, policy and endorsement issuance and regulatory compliance. We also review the inspection reports in order to verify construction type, proper insurance to value and that the inspector has not included recommendations that require immediate attention. Most importantly we confirm that the risk has been bound within the authority provided.<br />
							<div class="clear"></div>
