							<h5>claims</h5>
							Our claims review begins with consideration of timely notification and
coverage determination. We ensure each claim was properly investigated, that reserving for both loss and expense was prompt &amp; accurate and that handling was competent and in compliance with fair claims practice regulations. If a claim has been settled, we form a view as to whether the settlement was reasonable. If the claim is currently in litigation we assess the course and conduct of that litigation.<br />
<div class="clear"></div>							
