							<h5>finance &amp; administration</h5>
							Our financial accounting and administrative review assesses insurance knowledge and business skills. We look at all financial systems, procedures and practices. We audit such items as trust funds, bank statements, payable &amp; receivable accounts and review reinsurance advices &amp; collections. In our review of management, we take an overall look at an account and report upon the qualifications and performance of the personnel involved.<br />
